|I want live back Marilyn house.|| November 1975|| I want to go back<br>to Marilyn's house to live.
|-
|Genie Mama have a father<br>long time ago.|| December 1975|| N/A
|-
|Spool wind thread.|| December 1976|| N/A
|-
|Think about Mama love Genie.|| August 1977|| I am thinking about my wish {{sic|that<br>that fact}} that Mama loves Genie.
